-- Barclays Bank of Kenya says H1 pretax profit up 12 pct
-- 
-- Tue Aug 12, 2014 02:48AM EDT
-- None



NAIROBI, Aug 12 (Reuters) - Barclays Bank of Kenya's <BBK.NR> half year pretax profit rose 12 percent to 6.1 billion shillings ($69.36 million) compared to the the same period last year, largely due to a surge in customer loans, the bank said on Tuesday.

